day of the books we require.'),(18,1,'ArmsDealing18','Dec 2008, honor relationship with Nicolai, Gunter notified','unknown','set1','US GOVERNMENT TELEPHONE INTERCEPT: 15 DECEMBER 2008<br><br>Intercepted phone call from Boonmee Khemkhaengon to Lim Chanarong  December 15, 2008.  The caller says, “We will honor our relationship with Nicolai. “ The receiver says, “Arrangements are being made.  Gunter has been notified.” The caller says, “Then all is well.”'),(19,1,'ArmsDealing19','Dec 2008, Hakan, traveling books and cash to United Arab Emerites','unknown','set1','US GOVERNMENT TELEPHONE INTERCEPT:  [December 16 2008]<br><br>Call placed from a mobile phone (90-242-244-8945) registered in Antalya, Turkey to mobile phone (Hakan) registered in Istanbul, Turkey.  Conversation took place in the Kurmanji language on Wednesday, Tuesday, December 16, 2008 at 18:00:00 GMT.<br><br>90-242-244-8945:	I’m calling about the books we will order.  We will need cash to pay for them.<br>90-0212-516-90-24: You can’t bring that much money on the airplane.  It will look suspicious.<br>90-242-244-8945:	Can we pick the money up at a bank there?<br>90-0212-516-90-24: Probably.  Where are you traveling?<br>90-242-244-8945:	The United Arab Emerites.  Will that be a problem, Hakan?<br>90-0212-516-90-24: No, I do not think so.  I will check and let you know.  In the meantime, proceed with your arrangements.'),(20,1,'ArmsDealing20','Dec 2008, Saudi Arabian Bank transfer from SA80 to CH51','unknown','set1','US GOVERNMENT COMMUNICATION INTERCEPT:  [December 18 2008] Saudi Arabian Monetary Agency<br><br>Bank funds transfer information:<br><br>Transaction Identification Number:<br>From:  SA80 8000 0375 6080 2632 0160<br>To:	     CH51 0568 8001 1575 1710 0<br>Date:    11-21-08 11:57:37<br>Amount:  CHF77490.76'),(21,1,'ArmsDealing21','Dec 2008, Jordain Basel Private Bank SA Transfer','unknown','set1','US  GOVERNMENT COMMUNICATION INTERCEPT:  [December 19 2008] Jordain Basel Private Bank SA<br><br>Bank fun